<a aria-label="Discover Hidden Gems and Offbeat Adventures in Istanbul " class="nw_title_a" href="/news/discover-hidden-gems-and-offbeat-adventures-in-istanbul/"><h2 style="font-size: 21px!important;font-weight: bold;line-height: 27px;margin-bottom: 10px;;">Discover Hidden Gems and Offbeat Adventures in Istanbul </h2></a>
[⚠️] Unwanted space immediately before closing </a> tag
[Pages this occurred on]:
 - https://turkey-evisa.it.com/news/

[Line with Issue]:
<a href="/news/discover-hidden-gems-and-offbeat-adventures-in-istanbul/"><p class="news_cnt_p"> 
Ever thought about what else Istanbul has to offer beyond its famous spots like the Blue Mosque and Hagia Sophia? This city is full of surprises! If you’re itching to see a more authentic side, let’s dive into some hidden gems and offbeat adventures that will make your trip truly unforgettable. Don&amp;rsquo...</p></a>
[⚠️] Unwanted space immediately after opening <a> tag
[⚠️] Anchor text ends with punctuation: '.'
[Pages this occurred on]:
 - https://turkey-evisa.it.com/news/

[Line with Issue]:
